description:
In this coding challenge, I create a movie recommendation engine using the a "nearest neighbor" algorithm. In Part 1, I demonstrate you how to calculate a similarity score between two data points. This video is part of session 3 of my Spring 2017 ITP "Intelligence and Learning" course.

💻Challenge: https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/070.1-similarity-score.html
🎥Part 2: https://youtu.be/Lo89NLmSgl0
🎥Part 3: https://youtu.be/aMtckmWAzDg
